## Example Usage

```hcl
resource "appleappstoreconnect_subscription_group_submission" "premium" {
  subscription_group_id = appleappstoreconnect_subscription_group.premium.id

  # Ensure subscriptions, localizations and prices exist before submitting.
  depends_on = [
    appleappstoreconnect_subscription_localization.monthly_en,
    appleappstoreconnect_subscription_price.monthly_usd,
  ]
}
```

{{ .SchemaMarkdown | trimspace }}

## Import

Submissions can be imported using their ID:

```bash
terraform import appleappstoreconnect_subscription_group_submission.premium XXXXXXXXXX
```

~> **Note** Submitting is irreversible: a subscription group submission cannot be withdrawn through the API. Destroying this resource only removes it from Terraform state.
